{
    "name": "Ostrich",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Adult female ostriches average 6 feet tall and weigh about 220 pounds, with males averaging 7 to 9 feet and 250 pounds. Although they are likely to flee from predators when they can, ostriches are more than willing to stand and fight when trapped or defending their chicks; they\u2019re known to kick even lions to death in defense of their young.<br/><br/>A trained ostrich has a market price of 80 gp, whereas an egg is worth 25 gp. Because it\u2019s bipedal, an ostrich requires an exotic saddle."
        }
    ],
